<HEADLINE>
WHAT IF BRADLEY HAD CALLED GORE'S BLUFF? 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(jw) 
 By ADAM CLYMER    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   DES MOINES, Iowa _ On one level, Vice President Al Gore's
