children. Please, take the extra precautions if you have young ones
in your house, so you can all enjoy the holiday celebrations, the
family gatherings, the spirit of the season. Happy, healthy
holidays to all!
</P>
<P>
   _ Dr. Hank Clever, ``The Doctor Is In'' column, The St. Louis
Post-Dispatch &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
