   CHAMPAGNE (Undated) _ If you haven't already picked up a bottle
of your favorite bubbly to celebrate the millennium, don't be
surprised if you
</P>
<P>
   have to do some searching, pull a few more dollars out of your
</P>
<P>
   wallet, settle for your second choice. Or drink beer. By BILL
CITARA.
</P>
<P>
   STORAGE (Undated) _ With some tips and a little bit of
organization and common sense, storage can be safe and efficient.
First, make a storage plan and a list of what you want to keep,
store or get rid of. Then shop for containers and other storage
items that fit your needs. By FRANCES INGRAHAM HEINS.
