<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-27 13:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9926 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-STEM-RESEARCH-BOS &LR;      12-27 1672
