family effort to modify or eliminate the Republican platform plank
that calls for criminalizing all abortion, even one to save the
life of the mother. Bob Dole couldn't get rid of it in 1996, but
never underestimate Bar, let alone her son George W., the GOP
presidential frontrunner. By MARIANNE MEANS.
