<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Y2K CZAR REPORTS NO PANIC AS NEW YEAR LOOMS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
