</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-POLITICS (Jerusalem) _ The Shas political party, which
represents Sephardic Jews of Middle Eastern and North African
descent, announces that it has decided to quit the coalition
government of Israeli Prime Minister Ehud Barak; Barak asks Shas to
wait 24 hours and see what can be resolved. By Deborah Sontag. (The
