<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The following Arizona Republic story has been added for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for TUESDAY, DEC. 28 and
thereafter. If you have any questions, please contact the Republic
News Desk at (602) 444-8928.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
NEW&AMP;NOTABLE _ Anne Stephenson's capsule reviews of new books. By
ANNE STEPHENSON. Story will move in the ``E'' category.
